-- MOVES-Natixis appoints John Wade to its Asia Pacific team
-- 
-- Wed Jul 30, 2014 04:10AM EDT
-- None



July 30 (Reuters) - Natixis named John Wade as the head of its Syndicate/MTN desk, Asia Pacific, based in Hong Kong.

Wade will report to Devan Selvanathan, head of debt platform, Asia Pacific. Wade joins from Royal Bank of Scotland, where he was the head of debt capital markets, APAC.